    <lb n="1"/>Ἀπολινάρις Σονναῦτι τῷ <choice><corr>ἀδελφῷ</corr><sic>αδεφο</sic></choice> <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">χα</del>

    <lb n="2"/>πλεῖστα <expan>χα<ex cert="high">ίρειν</ex></expan>. κ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">αλ</supplied>ῶς ἔχι ἡ μήτηρ σου.

    <lb n="3"/>ἀμερίμνι περὶ τῶν ἱματίων σου,

    <lb n="4"/><choice><corr>ἐξετίναξα</corr><sic>εκσετιναξα</sic></choice> αὐτά. καλῶς ποιή-

    <lb n="5"/>σις λαβὼν τὸ σουβα<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">λά</supplied>ριόν μου

    <lb n="6"/>παρὰ τοῦ ὀνηλάτου τοῦ τὴν

    <lb n="7"/>πινακίδαν ἔχοντος καὶ πλ<add place="supralinear"><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ῆ</unclear></add>-

    <lb n="8"/>σόν μοι αὐτὸ ὑδάτους. εὑ-

    <lb n="9"/>ρεῖς δὲ <add place="supralinear">ἐ</add>ν τῇ σαργάνῃ πετα-

    <lb n="10"/>λίαν φοινικίων <choice><corr>ἣν</corr><sic>ο</sic></choice> ἐβάστα-

    <lb n="11"/>ξα <choice><corr>τῷ</corr><sic>το</sic></choice> ὤμῳ μου ἰς Ραειμα.

    <lb n="12"/>ἦλθον <choice><corr>καθῆσθαι</corr><sic>καθησται</sic></choice>. ἄσπαζε

    <lb n="13"/>Δημήτρειν.

    <lb n="14"/>ἔρρωσο.</ab></div><div n="meta.29693" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Ostrakon</rs></p></div><div n="meta.29693" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="126" notAfter="175">Mitte II</date></p></div><div n="meta.29693" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.29693" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">O.Claud.</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">276</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">29693</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0020</series>; <biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">276</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0020;2;276" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.29693" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">Planche XXIV</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.29693" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="high" full="yes">Raima</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>